text: Viva Bianca (or Viva Skubiszewski; 17 November 1983) is an Australian actress. She stars on the television show Spartacus. She was also on other shows. Her maiden name is pronounced scooby-shev-ski. She is from Victoria. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian movie actors Category:Actors from Victoria (Australia)
